snippet.title: Hasbi Rabbi- New Version by Two Little Sisters- Amber Younas & Aisha Younas
snippet.description:
The new version of the most popular Kalam Hasbi Rabbi Jal'Allah by two little sisters Amber Younas and Aisha Younas. Watch, like and share with your family and friends. 

Reciters: Amber Younas and Aisha Younas
Audio: Studio 92 UK
Mastered by rwds
